import Home from './routes/Home';
import Detail from './routes/Detail'
import {BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route} from 'react-router-dom'

function App() {
  return (<Router>
            <Switch>
              <Route path="/movie/:id">
                <Detail />
              </Route>
              <Route exact path="/">
                <Home />
              </Route>
            </Switch>
         </Router>)
}

export default App;
